law.catch_line: Effect Of Proceedings On Terms Of Sentence Imposed
law.text: [ Text of section added by 2012, 38 effective May 17, 2012.] Proceedings under this chapter shall not stay or otherwise interfere with a term of incarceration, parole, probation or other sentence imposed.
